        {
            "_id": "HtWDc7NVcwvkTHeP",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Shoulder Ballista",
            "sort": 700000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A shoulder ballista is an extension of the merztorlegon's body, functioning as a siege weapon that shares the demon's space, can't be targeted, and ceases to function after the merztorlegon's death. Either the merztorlegon or their siege crew can Aim or Load the ballista, but only the crew can Launch it.</p>\n<p><strong>Aim</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> 80 feet, minimum distance 30 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Load</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> (manipulate) 1 time</p>\n<p><strong>Launch</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> (attack, magical, manipulate, range increment 120 feet, unholy) 8d12 piercing, single target, @Check[reflex|dc:41]</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
